      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "id": "title",
          "text": "过年",
          "x": 25,
          "y": 20,
          "w": 30,
          "className": "cover-title",
          "audio": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "spread-01",
      "type": "spread",
      "ratio": "8:5",
      "background": "images/spread-01-bg.png",
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "id": "s1",
          "text": "山那边，有一种怪兽叫“年”。",
          "x": 57,
          "y": 21,
          "w": 35,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s2",
          "text": "冬天快结束的时候，年就醒了。",
          "x": 57,
          "y": 34,
          "w": 35,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "spread-02",
      "type": "spread",
      "ratio": "8:5",
      "background": "images/spread-02-bg.png",
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "id": "s1",
          "text": "年下山了。",
          "x": 61,
          "y": 18,
          "w": 31,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s2",
          "text": "村子里的人都关上门。",
          "x": 61,
          "y": 30,
          "w": 31,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s3",
          "text": "安安和宁宁躲在奶奶身后，偷偷往外看。",
          "x": 61,
          "y": 42,
          "w": 31,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "spread-03",
      "type": "spread",
      "ratio": "8:5",
      "background": "images/spread-03-bg.png",
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "id": "s1",
          "text": "奶奶说：“年怕红色，也怕响。”",
          "x": 56,
          "y": 18,
          "w": 36,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s2",
          "text": "爸爸点响了鞭炮，噼里啪啦！",
          "x": 56,
          "y": 31,
          "w": 36,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s3",
          "text": "年吓了一大跳，转身就跑。",
          "x": 56,
          "y": 44,
          "w": 36,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "spread-04",
      "type": "spread",
      "ratio": "8:5",
      "background": "images/spread-04-bg.png",
      "textBlocks": [
        {
          "id": "s1",
          "text": "天亮了，雪地上有一串大脚印。",
          "x": 65,
          "y": 13,
          "w": 30,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s2",
          "text": "大家一起吃饭，屋里暖暖的。",
          "x": 65,
          "y": 27,
          "w": 30,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        },
        {
          "id": "s3",
          "text": "从那以后，这一天就叫“过年”。",
          "x": 65,
          "y": 41,
          "w": 30,
          "className": "story-text",
          "audio": ""
        }
      ]
    },
